description:
A searcher for the TV show Psych.

Psychphinder is an app that will let you search quotes from all the episodes and movies of the TV show Psych.

🍍 Features 🍍

  • Search quotes from all the episodes and movies of Psych.
  • Save your favorite quotes.
  • Backup and restore your saved quotes.
  • View the references made in each episode.
  • Search what a reference means in your prefered search engine.
  • Share/save a quote as image or text.
  • Create wallpapers of your favorite quotes from the show.
  • Choose from the three themes available.

You can also share your backup file with others if you want, even between different platforms!
